OL,3,CLandowner targeted in fly-tipping
OL,4,C'epidemic'
OL,6,FHampshire landowner, Daniel Palmer,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News Meridian's Richard Slee
OL,8,Fthat repeated fly-tipping has cost him
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,11,FA land owner from Hampshire says he's
OL,12,Fbeen left thousands of pounds out of
OL,13,Fpocket after being targeted by fly-
OL,14,Ftippers.
OL,16,FTwo lorry loads of building waste was
OL,17,Fdumped on Daniel Palmer's land near
OL,18,FNorth Baddesley last month, the latest
OL,19,Fin a string of fly-tipping.
