OL,6,FThe council says it's investigating
OL,7,Fbut because the waste was dumped on
OL,8,Fprivate land Mr Palmer has to foot the
OL,9,Fbill for the clear up.
OL,11,FThe piles of rubbish, dumped last
OL,12,Fmonth, were discovered by a dog walker
OL,13,Fjust off Castle Lane at North
OL,14,FBaddesley.
OL,16,FThe entrance clearly states this is
OL,17,Fprivate land, which belongs to Dan
OL,18,FPalmer's family.
