OL,4,C'epidemic'
OL,6,FSearching through the rubbish, Dan
OL,7,Fcame across a lot of paperwork,
OL,8,Fincluding where it had come from.
OL,10,FSo he visited the homeowner in
OL,11,FEastleigh, who was aware of the fly
OL,12,Ftipping and gave Dan more information.
OL,14,F"I then spoke to the builder who
OL,15,Fadmitted he knew about it as well,
OL,16,Fobviously the jungle drums had been
OL,17,Fbeating and very quickly he said he
OL,18,Fpaid a couple of blokes to get rid of
OL,19,Fthe rubbish."
