OL,4,C'epidemic'
OL,6,FThis is now being investigated by Test
OL,7,FValley Council, but it's not the first
OL,8,Ftime this has happened at this
OL,9,Flocation.
OL,11,FThree years ago it was also a problem
OL,12,Fand so Test Valley Council put up
OL,13,Fhidden cctv cameras.
OL,15,FThey filmed a man who was fly tipping
OL,16,Fand he was sentenced to three months
OL,17,Fin prison and fined hundreds of pounds.
