OL,3,CLandowner targeted in fly-tipping
OL,4,C'epidemic'
OL,6,FDan says fly tipping is now at
OL,7,Fepidemic levels in the countryside,
OL,8,Fwhich is also the view of the Country
OL,9,FLand and Business Association, which
OL,10,Fis pleased that the local authority is
OL,11,Ftaking the lead in this investigation.
OL,13,FSouth East regional director, Tim
OL,14,FBamford, said, "Collectively over a
OL,15,Fyear we see about a million cases in
OL,16,FEngland and Wales, in Hampshire about
OL,17,F24 thousand cases and that's on public
OL,18,Fland but we think there is the same
OL,19,Fagain on private land. And this is a
OL,20,Fmassive issue.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
